<div dir="ltr">Hi Ralph,<div><br></div><div>This is regarding the MapReduce support with OpenMPI for which you gave a good amount of info previously. I have several MR applications that I&#39;d like to test for performance in an HPC cluster with OpenMPI. I found this presentation by you <a href="http://www.open-mpi.org/video/mrplus/Greenplum_RalphCastain-1up.pdf">http://www.open-mpi.org/video/mrplus/Greenplum_RalphCastain-1up.pdf</a>, but wonder if there&#39;s some detailed steps on getting a simple MR program running with OpenMPI.</div>
